        "uid": "73460"
      },
      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t租界多是一回事，租界質量是另外一回事，<br/>\n<br/>\n上海的International Settlement, French Concession在歷史書裡經常出現，相比而言天津漢口的就不如了，<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTc0YTFkMGUzMjdmMDc3OTFjYTU5LmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMjgwJmhlaWdodD03Njg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a74a1d0e327f07791ca59.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=768\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a74a1d0e327f07791ca59.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=768\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a74a1d0e327f07791ca59.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=768\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n這本書也蠻好，說的是白俄猶太男孩在上海最後的國際時期長大的故事，<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYTg4MGVmMWFjYmI1ZDJjYzM4NzM4LmpwZz93aWR0aD02OTUmaGVpZ2h0PTEwMDA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a880ef1acbb5d2cc38738.jpg?width=695&amp;height=1000\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a880ef1acbb5d2cc38738.jpg?width=695&amp;height=1000\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/a880ef1acbb5d2cc38738.jpg?width=695&amp;height=1000\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNGY1MmI0NDc5ODBjNDFmNGJlNDkzLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMDAwJmhlaWdodD03NDc\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4f52b447980c41f4be493.jpg?width=1000&amp;height=747\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4f52b447980c41f4be493.jpg?width=1000&amp;height=747\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/4f52b447980c41f4be493.jpg?width=1000&amp;height=747\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><br/>\n這部電影也是很不錯<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmMwM2NkMDY4ZmMxOTE5ZDA3YjAxLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xNTM2JmhlaWdodD0yMDQ4\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fc03cd068fc1919d07b01.jpg?width=1536&amp;height=2048\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fc03cd068fc1919d07b01.jpg?width=1536&amp;height=2048\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fc03cd068fc1919d07b01.jpg?width=1536&amp;height=2048\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZDdjMTkxZWM2ZDFiMGY4NTMyMzUxLmpwZz93aWR0aD03MjAmaGVpZ2h0PTM4MQ\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d7c191ec6d1b0f8532351.jpg?width=720&amp;height=381\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d7c191ec6d1b0f8532351.jpg?width=720&amp;height=381\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/d7c191ec6d1b0f8532351.jpg?width=720&amp;height=381\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZmEzNDBkM2YyNDI4NTgwMTY4NjAwLmpwZz93aWR0aD0xMjgwJmhlaWdodD03MjA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fa340d3f2428580168600.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=720\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fa340d3f2428580168600.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=720\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/fa340d3f2428580168600.jpg?width=1280&amp;height=720\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
